  "title": "QC Technician #75340",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Precision Manufacturing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>QC Technician</strong></li><li>Working Location: Loyang</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon - Fri, 8.00am - 5.45pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $2,000 + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and submit first article samples for approval.</li><li>Create packaging specifications.</li><li>Develop inspection plans for products.</li><li>Support inspection processes for in-process, incoming, and outgoing parts.</li><li>Train inspectors and operators on quality check points and measurement methods.</li><li>Work with Production, Toolroom, and Suppliers to address quality issues.</li><li>Ensure documents and records comply with ISO quality standards.</li><li>Assist Engineers as needed.</li><li>Manage and maintain all measuring and testing equipment.</li><li>Help Engineers update monthly quality control reports, such as supplier performance.</li><li>Assist Engineers or Managers in collecting and compiling data for reports.</li><li>Support other quality-related tasks as required.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 years of relevant experience.</li><li>Able to read engineering drawings.</li><li>Good reporting and administrative skills.</li><li>Able to work independently with minimal supervision.</li><li>Experience with OGP Smartscope, CMM, or other measuring tools.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#75340 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
